<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentdff1131c04b4402ab4e56b8bd00dcc12">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Pilgrim Hospital, Boston" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=827"/>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>This district general hospital was opened in 1976 to replace a number of small hospitals.</strong> It has a 24-hour major Accident and Emergency Department and all main specialties. <br/><br/>The hospital has recently undergone extensive redevelopment including a new maternity unit and women's health facilities.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
